Cấu trúc bảng
1 - users:
    id PK
    username
    password
    email
    full_name
    phone
    gender
    birthday
    address
    avatar_url
    role
    enabled
    disable_reason
    created_at
    updated_at

2. rooms:
    room_id PK
    room_name
    total_seats
    seats_x
    seats_y
    vip_seats
    couple_seats
    status

3. genres:
    genre_id PK
    genre_name

    Tại sao dùng Set?
    Quan hệ Many-to-Many không lưu dữ liệu trùng lặp. Set đảm bảo tính duy nhất của dữ liệu.
    List dùng khi cần thứ tự.
    VD: Genre: Action (1 phim có thể thuộc nhiều thể loại)

        Movies:
        - Avengers
        - Conan
        - Avengers

4. movies:
    movie_id PK
    title
    description
    duration
    release_date
    language
    poster_url
    trailer_url
    age_rating
    status
    created_at

5. movie_genres:
    movie_id FK
    genre_id FK

6. showtimes:
    showtime_id PK
    movie_id FK
    room_id FK
    start_time
    end_time
    ticket_price
    status

7. bookings
    booking_id PK
    user_id FK
    showtime_id FK
    booking_date
    total_amount
    payment_method
    booking_status
    booking_seat

Sơ đồ ERD
User
  |
  | 1
  |
  | N
Booking
  |
  | N
  |
  | 1
Showtime
  |
  +-------- N ------ 1 Movie
  |
  +-------- N ------ 1 Room

Movie
  |
  +-------- N ------ N Genre

  User      1 - N Booking
  Movie     N - N Genre
 ( @ManyToMany(mappedBy = "genres")
       private Set<Movie> movies;
 )
  Movie     1 - N Showtime
  Room      1 - N Showtime
  Showtime  1 - N Booking


